    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that starts up without hesitation. The interior is clean and free of any major stains or tears, though you might find some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from normal use. It\u2019s a dependable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner.",
