    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies dependable performance and a refined aesthetic. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a polished exterior finish, this automobile offers an exceptional balance of long-term value and sophistication for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
